data: Lift was a commercial health & wellness app curated for companies to customize their own wellness programs. Lift Mobile was the customer-facing app.
Lift CMS was the the desktop app that controlled the events and wellness programs behind the scenes.
Sage was a kiosk type application that aimed to address a prominent issue on how outpatients got their HMO approval slips.
Insight was an app back in 2016-2017 for Doctors to digitize their clinical practice and easily help them submit and track their HMO claims.
Easimed was the umbrella brand of my employer back in 2017. It was a team that served as a startup lab focused on enterprise healthcare applications.
